Message: The user completes the submission of the form
Do you have a way of sending giftcards to people to try out your platform
Currently, NewsBreak does not offer gift cards for trying out the platform. If you have any other questions or need assistance with something else, feel free to ask!
Do you have a way of Gifting someone currency to cover Ad costs?

Unfortunately, NewsBreak does not offer a way to gift currency or ad credits to cover ad costs for someone else. Ad credits are non-transferable and intended to be used solely within the account they were originally issued to. If you have any other questions, feel free to ask!
So ad credits are not transferrable?
That's correct, ad credits on NewsBreak are non-transferable and are intended to be used solely within the account they were originally issued to.
